WEBVTT

00:00:10.315 --> 00:00:12.859
{\an8}THE QUINCY EXTERMINATION OPERATION
FROM 1,000 YEARS AGO

00:00:13.193 --> 00:00:15.028
It wasn't 200 years ago?

00:00:16.905 --> 00:00:17.905
What's this...?

00:00:49.063 --> 00:00:53.775
{\an8}<i>The blue skies above are hopelessly clear</i>

00:00:53.900 --> 00:00:59.072
{\an8}<i>At my wit's end, I feel a growing frustration</i>

00:00:59.489 --> 00:01:03.911
{\an8}<i>As if to laugh at us hopeless cowards</i>

00:01:04.243 --> 00:01:07.664
{\an8}<i>Countless eyes stare at us</i>

00:01:08.081 --> 00:01:13.962
{\an8}<i>This soul of mine breaks again and again</i>

00:01:14.254 --> 00:01:17.215
{\an8}<i>All I can do is hold it tight</i>

00:01:18.424 --> 00:01:23.430
{\an8}<i>Until the day it turns to ash</i>

00:01:23.721 --> 00:01:26.308
{\an8}<i>I've absorbed all of this sorrow</i>

00:01:26.433 --> 00:01:30.938
{\an8}<i>It has shaped me, painted me</i>

00:01:31.105 --> 00:01:33.774
{\an8}<i>But that's how we got here, right?</i>

00:01:33.899 --> 00:01:38.736
{\an8}<i>One step at a time, just like breathing</i>

00:01:38.861 --> 00:01:41.281
{\an8}<i>These countless scars on my palm</i>

00:01:41.406 --> 00:01:43.283
{\an8}<i>That no longer fade</i>

00:01:43.408 --> 00:01:47.037
{\an8}<i>Are my badge, my story</i>

00:01:47.328 --> 00:01:50.998
{\an8}<i>I faced the fear and shred it to pieces</i>

00:01:51.125 --> 00:01:54.086
{\an8}<i>And let it walk beside me once more</i>

00:01:54.086 --> 00:01:58.841
{\an8}BLEACH: THOUSAND-YEAR BLOOD WAR

00:02:28.036 --> 00:02:31.455
It's been a thousand years,
hasn't it, Yhwach?

00:02:33.750 --> 00:02:36.502
I've come to put an end
to your life.

00:02:41.425 --> 00:02:42.967
Good indeed.

00:02:44.093 --> 00:02:46.930
It's always nice to see
one's spirits lifted.

00:02:47.681 --> 00:02:48.931
That is for certain.

00:02:49.724 --> 00:02:53.270
But you people...
have misjudged one thing.

00:02:54.062 --> 00:02:57.524
Your boss will lose to our boss.

00:02:58.400 --> 00:03:01.777
Because it's not just you people
whose spirits are lifted...

00:03:02.320 --> 00:03:04.364
from knowing that
our bosses are fighting!

00:03:04.823 --> 00:03:06.991
Die, old man!

00:03:12.580 --> 00:03:13.706
You're right.

00:03:13.706 --> 00:03:15.375
Someone misjudged.

00:03:17.085 --> 00:03:21.798
Your conventions
don't apply to Old Man Yama...

00:03:30.098 --> 00:03:31.933
Fools...!

00:03:33.018 --> 00:03:37.355
That's what they get
for interfering in my battle.

00:03:40.692 --> 00:03:43.027
What? You look like
you want to say something—

00:03:47.699 --> 00:03:48.699
Your Majesty!

00:03:51.245 --> 00:03:53.788
You haven't changed, Yhwach.

00:03:54.914 --> 00:03:58.502
But know that your habit of
selling your subordinates short...

00:03:58.961 --> 00:04:01.379
will end here.

00:04:03.464 --> 00:04:06.884
You've grown old,
Shigekuni Yamamoto.

00:04:07.677 --> 00:04:08.637
However...

00:04:08.637 --> 00:04:11.682
seeing you let your rage
take over like that...

00:04:11.682 --> 00:04:13.934
reminds me of when
you were younger.

00:04:14.141 --> 00:04:15.142
Nonsense!

00:04:51.512 --> 00:04:53.932
You've finally drawn it...

00:04:54.641 --> 00:04:58.269
You talk as if you've been
waiting for me to draw my sword.

00:04:58.769 --> 00:05:01.105
Do you know why I was waiting?

00:05:02.690 --> 00:05:05.985
Your flesh, blood, sword, and soul...

00:05:06.278 --> 00:05:09.822
I intend to crush you
until there's nothing left!

00:05:24.879 --> 00:05:26.213
<i>My throat feels dry...</i>

00:05:31.302 --> 00:05:34.305
My lips cracked open...

00:05:34.805 --> 00:05:36.182
Captain Unohana...

00:05:36.391 --> 00:05:39.353
Does your skin feel kind of dry
all of a sudden?

00:05:39.978 --> 00:05:41.271
Oh my, Isane.

00:05:41.271 --> 00:05:44.483
How cute of you
to worry about your skin.

00:05:44.733 --> 00:05:47.151
N-No, that's not what I meant...!

00:05:47.903 --> 00:05:50.447
<i>Please settle this quickly...</i>

00:05:50.822 --> 00:05:55.701
<i>before your power itself
destroys the Soul Society.</i>

00:06:00.247 --> 00:06:02.666
You can't use Hyorinmaru anymore.

00:06:03.209 --> 00:06:04.502
You've noticed, haven't you?

00:06:04.920 --> 00:06:07.129
Every drop of water
in the Soul Society

00:06:07.129 --> 00:06:09.882
is quietly evaporating
little by little.

00:06:10.634 --> 00:06:11.759
There's no mistake...

00:06:12.677 --> 00:06:13.637
This is...

00:06:16.305 --> 00:06:19.392
Bankai...
Zanka no Tachi!

00:06:21.937 --> 00:06:22.937
Bankai?

00:06:23.480 --> 00:06:26.733
That scorched little sword
is his Bankai?

00:06:27.067 --> 00:06:28.235
Don't underestimate it.

00:06:28.526 --> 00:06:32.738
Zanka no Tachi is a Bankai
that seals all of his flames

00:06:32.863 --> 00:06:34.658
within that single blade.

00:06:34.865 --> 00:06:36.701
One swing and it's all over.

00:06:37.201 --> 00:06:40.038
Everything it cuts is burnt by an explosive flame.

00:06:40.038 --> 00:06:41.790
It is a sword of hellfire.

00:06:41.915 --> 00:06:43.375
That's right...

00:06:43.708 --> 00:06:48.547
You've seen this Bankai
a thousand years ago, haven't you?

00:06:49.880 --> 00:06:51.757
But are you sure about that?

00:06:52.175 --> 00:06:56.721
Feel for yourself
whether it's still the same

00:06:56.721 --> 00:06:59.182
as a thousand years ago.

00:07:04.937 --> 00:07:05.896
<i>He cut me...!</i>

00:07:06.273 --> 00:07:08.358
<i>But where are the flames?</i>

00:07:08.733 --> 00:07:10.276
<i>Is his Bankai really different</i>

00:07:10.401 --> 00:07:12.903
<i>from the way it was
a thousand years ago?</i>

00:07:13.737 --> 00:07:16.074
<i>Flames are his Bankai's power.</i>

00:07:16.240 --> 00:07:17.867
<i>There's no mistake about that.</i>

00:07:17.867 --> 00:07:20.911
<i>Then, where did all that flame
disappear to?!</i>

00:07:29.295 --> 00:07:30.297
The tip of his sword!

00:07:31.005 --> 00:07:32.007
Correct!

00:07:41.016 --> 00:07:44.728
Zanka no Tachi, East!
Kyokujitsujin!

00:07:45.228 --> 00:07:48.564
I've focused
all the heat of my flames

00:07:48.564 --> 00:07:50.858
into just the tip of my blade.

00:07:51.817 --> 00:07:54.403
It does not burn,
nor does it emit an explosive flame.

00:07:54.778 --> 00:07:59.826
It merely blows away everything
it touches without a trace.

00:08:04.122 --> 00:08:06.290
All it means is that
I just have to cut you down

00:08:06.290 --> 00:08:08.668
without letting
your sword touch me!

00:08:16.091 --> 00:08:17.093
What?

00:08:19.136 --> 00:08:22.807
A thousand years ago,
all of you died.

00:08:28.187 --> 00:08:32.149
Today,
I will force you to remember...

00:08:32.817 --> 00:08:37.697
that all of you are nothing
but a horde of corpses

00:08:37.697 --> 00:08:40.158
just waiting to be burned!

00:08:46.914 --> 00:08:47.999
These flames...

00:08:48.416 --> 00:08:52.211
I just told you about
my Zanka no Tachi, East...

00:08:52.796 --> 00:08:55.215
If there is an East,
there is also a West.

00:08:58.051 --> 00:09:02.221
Zanka no Tachi, West.
Zanjitsu Gokui!

00:09:06.308 --> 00:09:10.397
Its heat...
is 15 million degrees Celsius.

00:09:11.398 --> 00:09:14.650
You can no longer touch me now.

00:09:14.859 --> 00:09:18.238
When I use my Bankai,
think of my body and blade

00:09:18.404 --> 00:09:21.365
as being enveloped by the sun.

00:09:22.701 --> 00:09:23.701
<i>Flames.</i>

00:09:24.369 --> 00:09:25.912
<i>15 million degrees Celsius...</i>

00:09:26.453 --> 00:09:30.542
<i>There's no way such immense heat
would be visible as flames.</i>

00:09:31.585 --> 00:09:32.793
<i>Is this an illusion?</i>

00:09:33.628 --> 00:09:34.629
<i>Wait...</i>

00:09:34.629 --> 00:09:39.466
<i>Perhaps his Spiritual Pressure
is so overwhelmingly powerful</i>

00:09:39.717 --> 00:09:42.928
<i>that it looks like flames
as it bursts out of him...</i>

00:09:44.264 --> 00:09:45.639
<i>Shigekuni Yamamoto!</i>

00:09:49.059 --> 00:09:50.061
Now then...

00:09:50.854 --> 00:09:53.188
I'm ending this, Yhwach.

00:09:53.856 --> 00:09:57.568
If I don't end this soon, you...

00:09:59.070 --> 00:10:02.407
and I, as well as the Soul Society,
will burn to ashes.

00:10:06.244 --> 00:10:07.578
"A thousand years ago,"

00:10:07.578 --> 00:10:09.956
"the Quincy empire
known as the Licht Reich"

00:10:10.289 --> 00:10:11.791
"intended to annihilate
all Hollows."

00:10:11.916 --> 00:10:14.628
"They invaded the Soul Society,
who had opposed them,"

00:10:14.961 --> 00:10:17.339
"but were wiped out by
the Thirteen Court Guard Squads..."

00:10:18.380 --> 00:10:19.758
"Then 200 years ago..."

00:10:20.174 --> 00:10:22.009
"The Soul Reapers
unilaterally decided to"

00:10:22.134 --> 00:10:24.428
"exterminate
the surviving Quincies,"

00:10:24.846 --> 00:10:27.724
"believing that they would disrupt
the circulation of souls."

00:10:29.183 --> 00:10:31.686
I guess this means that
no matter how much we try,

00:10:31.686 --> 00:10:34.397
Quincies and Soul Reapers
will never get along...

00:10:36.732 --> 00:10:40.986
<i>The Soul Society isn't involved,
but I'm still a Soul Reaper!</i>

00:10:41.363 --> 00:10:43.947
<i>No.
You're a Substitute Soul Reaper.</i>

00:10:44.740 --> 00:10:47.951
<i>Furthermore, the Soul Society
has abandoned you.</i>

00:10:50.205 --> 00:10:51.664
<i>I'm a Quincy.</i>

00:10:52.123 --> 00:10:54.668
<i>I cannot help Hollows or Arrancars.</i>

00:10:55.125 --> 00:10:56.126
<i>I know.</i>

00:10:56.503 --> 00:10:59.798
<i>Quincies exist
to destroy Hollows, right?</i>

00:11:00.756 --> 00:11:01.799
<i>Kurosaki...</i>

00:11:09.182 --> 00:11:10.767
<i>It feels like I'm burning...</i>

00:11:11.934 --> 00:11:14.687
<i>My eyes, my hair, my throat...</i>

00:11:14.854 --> 00:11:16.438
<i>If it weren't for Blut,</i>

00:11:16.438 --> 00:11:18.817
<i>I probably would have turned
into ashes even at this distance.</i>

00:11:19.024 --> 00:11:20.317
What's the matter?

00:11:20.485 --> 00:11:22.486
Are you just going to watch?

00:11:23.196 --> 00:11:26.865
Wait, that question
was a bit spiteful.

00:11:27.366 --> 00:11:29.994
Your sword is broken
and there's nothing you can do.

00:11:30.620 --> 00:11:32.831
I don't blame you
for not being able to move.

00:11:33.331 --> 00:11:35.082
You can run if you'd like.

00:11:35.875 --> 00:11:38.669
Except I'll quickly catch up
and kill you!

00:11:46.760 --> 00:11:48.263
Of course...

00:11:48.679 --> 00:11:50.514
Your sword is broken.

00:11:54.769 --> 00:11:59.691
All you have left are your arrows.

00:12:02.152 --> 00:12:03.235
Now then...

00:12:04.903 --> 00:12:06.530
Shall we?

00:12:08.741 --> 00:12:10.576
Kirchenlied...

00:12:14.581 --> 00:12:16.541
Sankt Zwinger!

00:12:17.750 --> 00:12:20.253
This is a Quincy's
ultimate defensive incantation

00:12:20.378 --> 00:12:21.754
that combines offense and defense!

00:12:21.921 --> 00:12:26.426
Step into this and you will be
torn apart by God's light!

00:12:26.676 --> 00:12:28.094
I told you, you cannot harm me!

00:12:31.931 --> 00:12:33.099
The dead...

00:12:33.807 --> 00:12:37.562
The ashes of those who perished
by my flame.

00:12:38.145 --> 00:12:39.355
Give me a hand...

00:12:39.855 --> 00:12:44.402
And I will give you
a moment's joy of battle.

00:12:47.113 --> 00:12:49.698
Zanka no Tachi, South...

00:12:55.996 --> 00:13:00.125
Kakajumanokushidaisojin!

00:13:09.552 --> 00:13:10.552
What is this?

00:13:11.846 --> 00:13:13.807
What in the world is this?!

00:13:18.061 --> 00:13:21.063
Kakajumanokushidaisojin...

00:13:21.605 --> 00:13:27.736
I awaken those I have slain by
heating their ashes with my blade.

00:13:28.278 --> 00:13:30.823
These awakened dead become my limbs

00:13:31.407 --> 00:13:35.953
and chase down those I deem to be
enemies until they turn into dust!

00:13:37.163 --> 00:13:39.706
How laughable that
the head of the Soul Reapers

00:13:39.706 --> 00:13:40.958
would awaken the dead!

00:13:41.375 --> 00:13:45.171
You don't deserve to be called
a Soul Reaper, Shigekuni Yamamoto!

00:13:45.547 --> 00:13:46.798
Don't think you can stop me...

00:13:47.673 --> 00:13:50.176
with something like this!

00:13:55.056 --> 00:13:59.936
Your mouth works well,
but your eyes don't work at all.

00:14:13.198 --> 00:14:14.366
Seydlitz...!

00:14:18.162 --> 00:14:20.163
Argola!
Hubert!

00:14:20.748 --> 00:14:24.043
Do you see the subordinates
that you mercilessly killed?

00:14:24.418 --> 00:14:26.837
Shigekuni Yamamoto, you bastard!

00:14:27.046 --> 00:14:31.884
Are you regretting not stealing
my Bankai earlier?

00:14:31.884 --> 00:14:33.010
No, that's not it.

00:14:33.427 --> 00:14:36.764
It's not that you decided
not to steal my Bankai.

00:14:36.931 --> 00:14:39.725
You <i>couldn't</i>.

00:14:40.018 --> 00:14:46.065
You people steal Bankai by learning
its power and understanding it.

00:14:46.356 --> 00:14:47.357
Am I wrong?

00:14:47.817 --> 00:14:51.738
I haven't shown my true power
even a thousand years ago.

00:14:52.029 --> 00:14:54.282
You cannot steal what is
beyond your understanding.

00:14:54.407 --> 00:14:55.866
It's as simple as that.

00:14:55.866 --> 00:14:57.451
Wait!
Where are you going?!

00:14:57.701 --> 00:14:59.037
Don't make a fuss.

00:14:59.037 --> 00:15:01.914
If you want to kill me,
then come after me.

00:15:01.914 --> 00:15:04.918
After you defeat your subordinates
who stand before you, that is.

00:15:04.918 --> 00:15:06.586
You bastard...

00:15:16.929 --> 00:15:21.475
It seems that even you still had
a shred of humanity left.

00:15:25.772 --> 00:15:28.524
Don't talk as if you know me!

00:15:28.732 --> 00:15:29.942
I thought I told you...

00:15:30.525 --> 00:15:35.280
don't assume you can stop me
with the likes of this!

00:15:41.370 --> 00:15:45.707
I can see your tears, Yhwach.

00:15:47.961 --> 00:15:49.294
Painful, isn't it?

00:15:49.711 --> 00:15:52.798
To have to destroy the corpses
of your subordinates...

00:15:52.798 --> 00:15:54.967
just to reach me.

00:15:55.969 --> 00:15:57.135
You must hate me, don't you?

00:15:57.552 --> 00:15:59.596
For using such a dirty tactic as

00:15:59.596 --> 00:16:02.933
bringing your dead subordinates
back to the battlefield.

00:16:04.977 --> 00:16:07.062
But none of what
you're experiencing...

00:16:07.062 --> 00:16:09.941
could compare to
the hatred and suffering...

00:16:10.066 --> 00:16:13.778
of the Soul Reapers
that you have killed!

00:16:17.447 --> 00:16:19.491
Zanka no Tachi, North...

00:16:20.701 --> 00:16:22.787
Tenchi Kaijin!

00:17:24.140 --> 00:17:29.394
I-I wasn't... strong enough...

00:17:30.730 --> 00:17:33.441
Please forgive me...

00:17:35.484 --> 00:17:38.403
<i>Wait, who would the boss
be apologizing to?</i>

00:17:39.154 --> 00:17:43.910
<i>This war was started by you.
And you've lost.</i>

00:17:44.160 --> 00:17:45.661
<i>Who are you apologizing to?</i>

00:17:46.996 --> 00:17:51.125
I wasn't able to...
carry out your orders...

00:17:51.625 --> 00:17:53.544
Who in the world are you?!

00:17:53.544 --> 00:17:55.462
Your Majesty Yhwach...!

00:17:59.424 --> 00:18:01.219
The Squad 1 Barracks...!

00:18:03.221 --> 00:18:04.305
Okikiba!

00:18:10.644 --> 00:18:12.814
Damn you, Yhwach...

00:18:12.814 --> 00:18:15.316
Stern Ritter "Y"...

00:18:15.982 --> 00:18:17.484
"The Yourself."

00:18:17.652 --> 00:18:19.403
The "R" of Royd Loyd.

00:18:20.695 --> 00:18:23.532
You made sure that no one noticed
I wasn't present.

00:18:24.075 --> 00:18:25.326
Well done.

00:18:27.702 --> 00:18:28.746
You...

00:18:29.622 --> 00:18:31.749
said... I did well...

00:18:32.375 --> 00:18:34.794
W-What an... honor to—

00:18:39.673 --> 00:18:41.092
You bastard...

00:18:41.675 --> 00:18:44.679
What have you been up to until now?

00:18:45.971 --> 00:18:48.849
What's beneath
the Squad 1 Barracks?

00:18:50.809 --> 00:18:53.061
The Central Underground
Great Prison!

00:18:54.689 --> 00:18:57.275
I went and met with Sosuke Aizen.

00:18:59.359 --> 00:19:03.071
{\an8}THE CENTRAL UNDERGROUND
GREAT PRISON

00:19:10.371 --> 00:19:11.622
Yhwach, huh?

00:19:12.999 --> 00:19:15.292
I have many ways of
finding out your name.

00:19:15.792 --> 00:19:18.671
Though I didn't think I would
get to see you with my own eyes...

00:19:19.881 --> 00:19:21.173
I won't ask why you're here.

00:19:22.090 --> 00:19:24.551
The unpleasant Spiritual Pressure
swirling on the surface above

00:19:24.551 --> 00:19:26.261
is enough to tell me
what is happening.

00:19:26.721 --> 00:19:28.722
In that case,
this simplifies things.

00:19:29.557 --> 00:19:32.977
One of the Special Threats,
Sosuke Aizen...

00:19:33.728 --> 00:19:35.645
come under my command.

00:19:36.646 --> 00:19:41.234
The Quincy King is welcoming me
into the Wandenreich?

00:19:42.403 --> 00:19:44.614
We share the same path—

00:19:44.614 --> 00:19:48.617
the goal of destroying
the Soul Society, don't we?

00:19:49.618 --> 00:19:50.952
The same path, huh?

00:19:53.038 --> 00:19:54.039
I refuse.

00:19:54.664 --> 00:19:55.665
What?

00:19:56.709 --> 00:19:58.501
I cannot stand to see
the Quincy King

00:19:58.501 --> 00:20:00.712
following in the footsteps
of a Soul Reaper.

00:20:02.548 --> 00:20:04.592
Is that your answer?

00:20:07.510 --> 00:20:09.055
We're done talking here.

00:20:10.932 --> 00:20:12.266
Are you leaving already?

00:20:13.643 --> 00:20:17.855
You came here because you saw
my power as a threat, didn't you?

00:20:18.772 --> 00:20:19.773
That's right.

00:20:20.066 --> 00:20:23.152
But since you are fused
with the Hogyoku,

00:20:23.277 --> 00:20:25.028
it would take too long to kill you

00:20:25.028 --> 00:20:27.990
or take you with us
to restrain you.

00:20:28.699 --> 00:20:30.159
A wise decision.

00:20:31.326 --> 00:20:34.747
It is best to minimize the time
we spend sharing the same path.

00:20:35.623 --> 00:20:36.915
Especially when
dealing with someone

00:20:36.915 --> 00:20:38.584
who should eventually
be eliminated.

00:20:47.926 --> 00:20:49.095
Now then...

00:20:49.261 --> 00:20:53.641
I see you've exhausted your powers
in your battle with my impostor.

00:20:54.141 --> 00:20:55.977
Haven't you, Shigekuni Yamamoto?

00:20:56.519 --> 00:20:58.813
Shut up!
Bankai!

00:21:05.903 --> 00:21:09.030
It's not that we couldn't steal
your Bankai.

00:21:09.656 --> 00:21:14.662
But your power is so strong that
no one other than I can handle it.

00:21:15.203 --> 00:21:20.625
Therefore, I ordered Royd
to leave it alone until I returned.

00:21:21.251 --> 00:21:22.295
So what now?

00:21:22.420 --> 00:21:24.797
I can use the power of this Bankai

00:21:25.298 --> 00:21:29.343
to awaken the corpses
of your subordinates,

00:21:29.844 --> 00:21:32.012
Genryusai Yamamoto.

00:21:32.471 --> 00:21:33.806
You bastard!

00:21:59.999 --> 00:22:03.711
Farewell, Shigekuni Yamamoto.

00:22:28.234 --> 00:22:31.238
{\an8}<i>Everything we had left behind</i>

00:22:31.404 --> 00:22:35.576
{\an8}<i>Our breaths blending as mist</i>

00:22:35.576 --> 00:22:39.997
{\an8}<i>without form or expression</i>

00:22:40.122 --> 00:22:44.292
{\an8}<i>We lie buried as we glare
into the distance</i>

00:22:44.626 --> 00:22:47.253
{\an8}<i>I can't hear anything</i>

00:22:47.380 --> 00:22:50.508
{\an8}<i>I can't seem to cut anything</i>

00:22:50.633 --> 00:22:53.009
{\an8}<i>It feels like I'm sinking</i>

00:22:53.009 --> 00:22:54.970
{\an8}<i>Falling, falling</i>

00:22:54.970 --> 00:22:56.055
{\an8}<i>Touching</i>

00:22:56.055 --> 00:22:59.642
{\an8}<i>Eyes struck wide open</i>

00:22:59.642 --> 00:23:02.894
{\an8}<i>Something no one has ever seen</i>

00:23:02.894 --> 00:23:09.276
{\an8}<i>The furthest reaches are now visible to us</i>

00:23:09.652 --> 00:23:13.279
{\an8}<i>It cannot be undone
and cannot be stopped</i>

00:23:13.279 --> 00:23:16.534
{\an8}<i>This ensuing struggle</i>

00:23:16.784 --> 00:23:21.497
{\an8}<i>Whisk it away beyond
the ends of the earth</i>

00:23:21.663 --> 00:23:23.665
{\an8}<i>Along with our breaths</i>

00:23:23.874 --> 00:23:25.166
{\an8}<i>Take everything</i>

00:23:25.166 --> 00:23:29.922
{\an8}<i>Whisk it away beyond
the ends of the earth</i>

00:23:30.047 --> 00:23:31.965
{\an8}<i>Along with our futures</i>

00:23:32.090 --> 00:23:33.843
{\an8}<i>Along with our world</i>

00:23:34.926 --> 00:23:38.138
{\an8}<i>Something no one has ever seen</i>

00:23:38.305 --> 00:23:44.644
{\an8}<i>The furthest reaches are now
visible to us</i>

00:23:44.644 --> 00:23:46.646
{\an8}<i>Don't you know God's demand?</i>

00:23:46.771 --> 00:23:48.523
{\an8}<i>Don't you know God's demand?</i>

00:23:48.648 --> 00:23:52.027
{\an8}<i>As we tear each other down</i>

00:23:59.201 --> 00:24:01.871
<i>"A petal falling,
never to bloom again."</i>

00:24:03.079 --> 00:24:06.541
<i>"A petal in flames,
full of beauty."</i>

